## 🏷️ **Key Details**

- **Full Name:** William Edward Burghardt Du Bois
- **Born:** February 23, 1868 – Great Barrington, Massachusetts, USA
- **Died:** August 27, 1963 – Accra, Ghana
- **Education:**
    - Fisk University (B.A.)
    - Harvard University (M.A., Ph.D.) – First African American to earn a Ph.D. from Harvard
